room_title: Escape room "Butcher Shop" by Mission X Escape in Raleigh - Durham
review: Tried out the Butcher Room with some friends and had such a fun time! It was exciting down to the last minute, and we just barely made it out! The clues were a perfect difficulty, and the room was totally decked out! Planning on coming back soon!

room_title: Escape room "Butcher Shop" by Mission X Escape in Raleigh - Durham
review: We had so much fun!!! The employees were very professional and friendly and the game was very enjoyable. We did Butcher Shop and it was hard but I loved it!

room_title: Escape room "Butcher Shop" by Mission X Escape in Raleigh - Durham
review: I failed but it was bitter sweet the staff was helpful  and friendly they really made the experience worth while
